4. 以下为存在微妙错误的参考实现，要求定位所有错误原因、修正错误，并给出完全符合约束的正确实现代码：
```javascript
const orderDiscountPipeline = (discountRules) => {
  return (thresholdConfig) => {
    return (orders) => {
      return orders.map(order => {
        // 计算生效折扣率
        const matchedDiscounts = discountRules.filter(([ruleName, rate]) => 
          order.tags.includes(ruleName.toLowerCase())
        );
        const finalRate = matchedDiscounts.length > 0 ? Math.min(...matchedDiscounts.map(([, r]) => r)) : 1;
        // 计算折后价
        const afterDiscount = order.originalPrice * finalRate;
        // 计算满减金额
